# --------------------------------------------------
# Chat Runtime Framework (Internal)
#
# These files remain private until the Avatar Runtime
# migration and framework documentation are ready for
# public release.
# --------------------------------------------------

# Internal framework documentation
framework/**/*.md
!framework/README.md
framework/templates/



# Local engineering verification and private compatibility dependencies.
# Keep these directories on the development machine, but do not publish them.
/framework/build-prompts/
/framework/verification/
/player/
/deployment/

# Root Markdown files are private/internal by default.
# README.md and the required public modification notice remain public.
# AI_BOOTSTRAP.md therefore stays local and ignored.
/*.md
!README.md
!MODIFICATIONS.md

